{"lang": "ja_JP", "eventid": "main_16", "eventName": "背理分光", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "16-9", "avgTag": "戦闘後", "storyName": "狂人の弁解", "storyInfo": "正気を失った坑夫は、ここにいる村人を殺さねばならないと固く決心した。車両を奪ったあの時、実の息子を殺したのと同じように。村全体を巻き込む大火事の中、ランキンは己の悪夢が現実になったと錯覚していた。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormflp", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "sn"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "sn", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g14_ursusvillage", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ウルサスの晩秋。夜の気温は急激に下がる。吹き荒れる寒風が枝の上に積もった雪をぱらぱらと吹き落とす。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "広場から人影はとうに消え、遠くに点在する低い家々にも明かり一つすらも見えなかった。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "広場中央の焚火を見ると、焼け焦げた薪の上にわずかに火が残っている。火種は北風に何度も引っ掻かれながら、かろうじて最後の息吹を留めていた。"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "sn", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_firewood_throw", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_warmbonfire_loop", "loop": "true", "channel": "a", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一本の太い薪が火の中に放り込まれると、火花が空中に舞い上がった。"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1971_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奴らは……", "name": "ホーリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "俺たちの行方を知った。", "name": "ホーリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "炭の中に横たわる乾いた薪が、徐々に黒く燻され、形を変えた後、突如立ち上った炎に完全に呑み込まれた。"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "火明かりが弱り果てた感染者の顔を映し出す。だが彼が温もりを感じることは微塵もなかった。"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1971_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あいつら。ここにいる……みんな。", "name": "ホーリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あいつらを皆殺しにしないと……ガネアを粛清したように……", "name": "ホーリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1971_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そうすればあいつらは……", "name": "ホーリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#7$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "道徳をなくすことも、純潔に背くことも……", "name": "ホーリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#7$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "魂を汚すこともなくなる。", "name": "ホーリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#7$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "男は痛みを感じた。まるで心臓が針で貫かれたような痛みだ。"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "男は寒さにこごえた。凍てつく湖に落ちたような、震えの止まらぬ寒さだ。"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彼には炎が必要だった。"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_firewood_throw", "volume": 0.2}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_firewood_throw", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_firewood_throw", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一本、二本、三本。"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一束、二束、三束。"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "元々かろうじて燃えていた火種が木の隙間から噴き出し、灼熱の悪夢と化した。その炎は火を熾した者の身体に突き立たんばかりだった。"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "痩せ衰えた坑夫は燃える木の棒を拾い上げると、静まり返った家々へと向かっていく。"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "sn", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_newiceforest_3", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "sn", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "トン、タッ。トン、タッ。"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "軽やかな音、重い音。強い音、弱い音。規則正しい足音が響く。"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1971_1#4$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眠っている……眠っている！", "name": "ホーリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#4$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "みんな眠っている。", "name": "ホーリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#4$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "お前たちは自分がこれからどんな目に遭うか、どんな裁きを受けるかを知らないんだ。", "name": "ホーリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#4$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1971_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感染者を助けて、匿い、そして売る。まるで駄獣のように従順で、無知な奴らめ！", "name": "ホーリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#5$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1971_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "だが、構わない。", "name": "ホーリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "俺がお前らを助けてやる。俺ならお前らを助けられるさ。", "name": "ホーリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1971_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……なぜなら俺は黙して祈り……", "name": "ホーリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#2$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "お前らの苦しみを……", "name": "ホーリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#2$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1971_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "共に担うからだ。", "name": "ホーリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#6$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "狂人は恐怖の松明を握り締めたが、そのかすかな炎では、彼が感じていた寒さを抑えきれなかった。"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彼は骨の髄まで冷え込むような寒さを感じていた。その寒さは鉱石病から、寒風から、そしてウルサスから来ていた。"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彼には、より多くの炎が必要だった。"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "突如、彼の目の前に大量の干し草が現れた。"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1971_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "炎。", "name": "ホーリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彼は松明を放り投げた。"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1971_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "浄化――", "name": "ホーリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#4$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "炎が朽ちたものすべてを呼び起こす。"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1971_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "救済！", "name": "ホーリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1971_1#5$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "sn", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$firestorm", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$m_bat_act37d0d0_01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_062cg_phantom_front", "fade": "true", "fadetime": 1.5, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_churchfire", "loop": "true", "channel": "a", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.7, "fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彼はかつてないほど、はっきりと生を実感していた。"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g10_tent_inside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1963_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,-50", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "脳内でうなり声が響き続けている。ランキンは悪夢の中で、己の感覚と理性を取り戻そうとしていた。"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "五感は回復しつつあったが、悲鳴はなおも消えず、むしろどんどん近づいてくる。"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彼は力を振り絞って立ち上がり、覚束ない足取りでテントの外に出て、新鮮な空気を一口吸おうとした。"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_smoke_01", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snowconutry_3", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_churchfire", "loop": "true", "channel": "a", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "と、灼熱の空気が襲い掛かり、身体中の冷や汗が瞬時に蒸発する。"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一瞬にしてすべての感覚が戻り、感覚器官から伝わる情報がランキンに押し寄せた。"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ここは夢の中ではない、現実だ。悪夢で見た光景が現実として続いている。"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "周囲は逃げ惑う人々であふれ、かつて安らぎをもたらしていた家屋は、今や完全に炎に呑み込まれていた。"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "立ち上る濃煙の中で、焼け焦げた絶望の匂いが獣の爪のように皆の喉を締め付ける。その暴威の下では、人間は蟻のようにちっぽけな存在に感じられた。"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1967_1#5$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ランキン！", "name": "ニクト"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1967_1#5$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1963_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何が……起きたんだ？", "name": "ランキン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#6$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1967_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "わからない、急に火の手が上がったんだ。こんな勢いじゃとても消せやしない！", "name": "ニクト"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1967_1#5$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "とりあえずみんなを避難させないと！", "name": "ニクト"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1967_1#5$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.6}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1963_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ランキン、交換してもらった食糧がまだ建物に残ったままだ。中に入って取ってこなきゃ――", "name": "興奮した坑夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1963_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そんなことを気にしている場合か！", "name": "ランキン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#7$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "皆を起こせ！　全員村の外まで避難させるんだ！　早く、急げ！", "name": "ランキン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#7$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "しかしランキンが声を張り上げても火災現場の群衆が秩序を取り戻すことはなく、恐怖だけが止めようのない勢いで広がっていった。"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "channel": "a", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$flashback", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "avg_8_30", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.05, "yScaleFrom": 1.05, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 1.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奴は初めから……"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死んでいなかった。"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$flashback", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_smoke_01", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snowconutry_3", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1963_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "channel": "a", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "いや、違う……俺は勝った、奴を殺したんだ！", "name": "ランキン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#7$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "俺は皆を救えるんだ……！", "name": "ランキン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#7$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "r"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "r", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4207_branch_1#6$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生！", "name": "ヴェトチキ"}, "figure_art": "avg_4207_branch_1#6$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1963_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ヴェトチキ、なぜここに？　早く安全な場所へ逃げろ！", "name": "ランキン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#6$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4207_branch_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生、わ、わたし……！", "name": "ヴェトチキ"}, "figure_art": "avg_4207_branch_1#10$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1963_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "俺の言うことが聞けないのか！？", "name": "ランキン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#7$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ランキンはヴェトチキの手を振り払おうとしたが、少女は全力で彼の腕を掴んだ。"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4207_branch_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "おばあちゃんが、おばあちゃんが、い、いないんです！", "name": "ヴェトチキ"}, "figure_art": "avg_4207_branch_1#10$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1963_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "なに……？　一緒にいたんじゃなかったのか？", "name": "ランキン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#6$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吃音の少女は両手を使って何があったのか説明しようとしたが、話を聞くまでもなく彼女の恐怖の表情がすべてを物語っていた。"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1963_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ニクト！", "name": "ランキン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#5$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "お前は皆の避難を続けろ。俺はヴェトチキとナディア夫人を探しに行く！", "name": "ランキン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#5$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1967_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "わ、分かった！", "name": "ニクト"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1967_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ランキンとヴェトチキは炎の中を駆け抜けた。両側の家屋は炎に包まれており、少しでも気を抜けば、衣服にまで燃え移りそうだ。"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4207_branch_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "おばあちゃん……うっ、うっ、おばあちゃん！", "name": "ヴェトチキ"}, "figure_art": "avg_4207_branch_1#10$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ランキンも大声で叫ぼうとしたが、胸中に渦巻く無力感が彼の喉を塞ぎ、声を出すことも、息をすることも困難にさせた。"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "これほど激しい火の手が、行動を制限された老人にとって何を意味するか、彼はよく分かっていた。"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4207_branch_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "せ、先生、わたし……先生……うっ……うっ！", "name": "ヴェトチキ"}, "figure_art": "avg_4207_branch_1#10$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黒煙が立ち込める十字路で、ヴェトチキは手で口元を抑えながら、ランキンを指差した後、分かれ道を指差した。"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1963_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "だ、ダメだ……ヴェトチキ、俺から離れて動いちゃダメだ……言うことを聞け……", "name": "ランキン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#10$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4207_branch_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生！", "name": "ヴェトチキ"}, "figure_art": "avg_4207_branch_1#10$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "顔を紅潮させた少女の目から、大粒の涙がこぼれ落ちた。そのまま彼女は両手を組むと、祈りの仕草を取った。その姿は奇妙ではあったが、敬虔さが感じられた。"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彼女が祈る相手は皇帝でも佯狂者でもない。少女はただ、ランキンの助けを願った。"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1963_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "俺は……", "name": "ランキン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#3$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "channel": "a", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$flashback", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "avg_8_29", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.05, "yScaleFrom": 1.05, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 1.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "愚かな。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}},